{"tid":123034,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"港台31 - 世情2 (追夢者)","createTime":"2017-02-16T13:44:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T14:02:32.000Z","uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"53154266745f68cf78d3c24f1d10a576edacf71b","tid":123034,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T13:44:30.000Z","msg":"追夢者<br />\n<br />\n洪都拉斯和薩爾瓦多的青少年每日面對黑幫的威嚇，他們為了尋找更好的生活，紛紛偷渡往美國。在美國，每月就有超過5千名非法移民青年或兒童被捕。記者採訪兩個15歲洪都拉斯青年。他們由墨西哥邊境爬上火車頂，準備偷渡去美國，過程驚險萬分。"},{"pid":"ff49c85106b69aa84975cf35c63a69d91068c2aa","tid":123034,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T13:47:22.000Z","msg":"講墨仔偷渡美國 好恐怖 唔怪得川普會贏到大選"},{"pid":"ca9ab7146976c3d22e7adbd0a5bab730585786e1","tid":123034,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T13:53:14.000Z","msg":"成班蝗蟲心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45e5fc9d3d850ae48311a2236a2bc37356c517b","tid":123034,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T14:00:42.000Z","msg":"完"},{"pid":"bd8e898f67344873cbabbb6a4495271dd77298a6","tid":123034,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:26:52.000Z","msg":"今集有香港"},{"pid":"a42759864f6e5d1ba96cd2516d3ccebfc2320bb9","tid":123034,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T14:02:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今集有香港</blockquote><br />\n係 柬埔寨太空計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}